image.characterName: モブ HK_筋肉おやじ（大）01-1

parameters: ストーリー　セレナ売ります
\n< Serena >.......
\n< Male >Well, adventurer. I have a question for you.
\n< Male >Do you understand what you have done...?
\n< Serena >I did the right thing.
\n< Male >I see.

\n< Male >An unsuitable task has been assigned to an
unsuitable person.
\n< Male >Accidents are exactly what happen like that.
\n< Male >It's a big loss. A significant loss.

\n< Male >The total debt held by the women who ran away is
58,000 S.

\n< Male >The opportunity loss caused by this incident is
approximately 300,000 S.

\n< Male >Furthermore, you have an obligation to pay a
penalty of 800,000 S for violations of the first,
third, and fourth provisions.

\n< Male >The total is 1,103,800 S. Taking into account the
future losses that this case will bring to the
guild, your debt to the guild has now reached
2,000,000 S.
\n< Male >Any objections?
\n< Serena >No.
\n< Male >Oh?

\n< Serena >I did what I had to do. There's nothing to be
ashamed of.

\n< Serena >You should do what you should do. That's what
fairness is, right?

\n< Male >...Do you have any intention of repaying such a
large amount of money on your own?
\n< Serena >Not at the moment. Unfortunately not.

\n< Serena >Of course, if I can continue being an adventurer,
I have confidence that I will eventually be able
to repay it.
\n< Male >Of course, that choice is impossible.

\n< Male >However, if that's the case, we will have no
choice but to lay our hands on your only capital,
which is your body.
\n< Male >The problem is how to convert it into cash.
\n< Subordinate >Boss.
\n< Male >I understand.

\n< Male >...Adventurer Serena. As a measure against the
losses this time, we will strip you of your status
as your own master.

\n< Male >From today onwards, you will be classified as an
urban slave, and your qualification as a master
will be put up for auction to compensate for the
losses.

\n< Serena >Me, a slave? According to the church law, owning
slaves within the kingdom is supposed to be
prohibited.

\n< Male >You will become an urban slave. As long as you are
in the city, your freedom to move, act, and own
property will be restricted.

\n< Male >This is not a forbidden slave according to the
church. The words are similar... Oh, I just
realized. This is not good... It's a misleading
expression.

\n< Male >There may be corrections in the future. But for
now, you have become a status called an urban
slave.
\n< Serena >...They are a bunch of unbearable idiots.

\n< Serena >Fine. Do as you please, whether it's slavery or
auctioning me off.

\n< Serena >However, no matter what happens to my title, I am
still myself. I will not be treated like a wolf on
a leash with a dog collar.

\n< Male >If you're a smart wolf, you should be satisfied
with a dog collar. If you know that it can get
even worse.
\n< Male >Take me with you.
\n< Subordinate >Hah!
